snippet.title: Wendy Williams Speaks On Her Show Getting Cancelled
snippet.description:
Wendy Williams Speaks On Her Show Getting Cancelled

Is Wendy Williams about to be cancelled just like her rival Ellen DeGeneres?
Wendy is no stranger to controversial comments but she really crossed the line this time and the fans are now demanding for her show to be cancelled.
Wendy is now reportedly panicking that her time is up and sources say she’s cracking under pressure.
So what did Wendy say this time and will she really get cancelled?
